{"tid":2224894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專頁籲國際關注  李宇軒妹：我唔救邊個救","createTime":"2020-10-01T02:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:24:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d04715f750170c9df7ada93fe7a60e9a4d11c3f9","tid":2224894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/MDF3SCS7MBD6PFI2HBXBA5X62I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FMDF3SCS7MBD6PFI2HBXBA5X62I%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kymCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=3e04229d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FMDF3SCS7MBD6PFI2HBXBA5X62I%2F&h=0be02f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/MDF3SCS7MBD6PFI2HBXBA5X62I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n專頁籲國際關注 <br />\n李宇軒妹：我唔救邊個救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r2ekMLtZzeInoE3Z16NVT3NJqAo=/1257x643/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V5JPHWMFGJDY3PDF4O24QXDMUQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr2ekMLtZzeInoE3Z16NVT3NJqAo%3D%2F1257x643%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV5JPHWMFGJDY3PDF4O24QXDMUQ.png&h=8c3744d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李小姐在fb專頁上載李宇軒（右圖）在日本拍攝的照片，並附上歌詞表達對哥哥的思念。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港故事成員李宇軒8月10日與壹傳媒黎智英等涉違反國安法被捕，兩周後與其他11人涉偷渡往台灣被中國海警截獲，生死未明。拔萃男書院畢業的李宇軒，在妹妹眼中是「叻人」，即使接連的壞消息險些打沉她，但想到哥哥為理想努力的樣子，又重新燃起勇氣，更開設facebook 專頁和Twitter賬戶，希望引起更多國際關注，或者行動會令她陷入困境也不退縮，「佢係我屋企人，我唔救佢邊個救佢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無懼陷違國安法困境<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒中學畢業於名校拔萃男書院，被捕前是程式編寫員，在反修例運動前未有明顯政治參與，李宇軒妹妹昨接受。。。。。。。。。。。。，「如果係功利、自私嘅人，佢就唔需要去理呢啲嘢，佢可以有好嘅生活、好嘅事業，亦都可以置身事外&hellip;&hellip;我覺得係無私嘅付出，可以話係不求回報，好努力咁去追求佢理想中嘅事」。<br />\n<br />\n即使時光重來，李小姐也會鼓勵哥哥繼續為所信的理想努力，她一再強調哥哥所做的，在今年7月1日後根本沒違反國安法，若然以他之前的行為提告，即沒追溯期是「講大話」。<br />\n<br />\n在李宇軒失蹤後幾日，李小姐開設了「Andy is Missing」專頁，以英文寫作，打正旗號呼籲國際關注事件。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「咁即係全面噤聲，一啲嘢都唔可以講，係唔係變成咁呢」。更大的勇氣來自血濃於水的手足之情，李小姐哽咽說：「我諗係血濃於水，佢係我屋企人，我唔救佢邊個救佢？」<br />\n<br />\n過去幾星期，。。。。。。。。。。。。，「做咗唔一定有用，但係唔做就一定冇用，就好似反修例運動咁，成日都會有人問遊行有冇用，但係當大家都唔踏出第一步，就唔會有改變」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"c784e3d7fc4623b8097fb573aa62a3297d7233d0","tid":2224894,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b74272f75115db7891c692b9f53bd4c7e69d608","tid":2224894,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de15f62298a0a47e29ac0dfcae51f8a4e12f373","tid":2224894,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60a3c3c592692e7c393fa84b8f1031c93d5a1b9","tid":2224894,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fb209dd419e58a2084e10113089055a46e39325","tid":2224894,"uid":295112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19c277c946728ca85c304a6376cc59ed72508a07","tid":2224894,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由之歌】有個香港人無收錢整咗條咁嘅片出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2224648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2224648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b16b139b0c26a7fda88e41d13b248164dd9ee4ec","tid":2224894,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2b8a1d9ea23ec5390abbc6217fb831ede8e19fe","tid":2224894,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime